      "updated": 1777243533475,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Class Camera -> handles the camera which follows the\nplayer around.\n\nClass Map -> handles map drawing.\n\nfunction load_maps -> keeping all maps as return from\nthis function avoid the problem from pygame attempting\nto use the convert() method before the display screen\nfrom main.py was created.",
      "fontSize": 19.028338790651038,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Class Camera -> handles the camera which follows the\nplayer around.\n\nClass Map -> handles map drawing.\n\nfunction load_maps -> keeping all maps as return from\nthis function avoid the problem from pygame attempting\nto use the convert() method before the display screen\nfrom main.py was created.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
