      "updated": 1777244287619,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Class Menu, base class for all menus. Handles button \ncreation, drawing and handle key presses or mouse clicks.\n\nClass MainMenu -> main menu class, with start, options\nand quit buttons.\n\nClass OptionsMenu -> options, for now only allows the\ndifficulty change. TODO: add a key remaping option, \nmaybe a screen resizing option and a volume change.\n\nClass PauseMenu -> menu that appears when the game\nin the PLAY state is paused. For now, this allows to\nchange the song to be played. TODO: improve the \nsongs list, maybe creating a pagination or scrolling\nfunctionality. Perhaps add an option for free play,\ninstead of allowing playing in the exploration mode.\n\n",
      "fontSize": 19.028338790651038,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Class Menu, base class for all menus. Handles button \ncreation, drawing and handle key presses or mouse clicks.\n\nClass MainMenu -> main menu class, with start, options\nand quit buttons.\n\nClass OptionsMenu -> options, for now only allows the\ndifficulty change. TODO: add a key remaping option, \nmaybe a screen resizing option and a volume change.\n\nClass PauseMenu -> menu that appears when the game\nin the PLAY state is paused. For now, this allows to\nchange the song to be played. TODO: improve the \nsongs list, maybe creating a pagination or scrolling\nfunctionality. Perhaps add an option for free play,\ninstead of allowing playing in the exploration mode.\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
